%20exploding%20packages%20on%20flights%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20in%20Copenhagen.%20Around%208%3A30%20p.m.%20on%20a%20Monday%20in%20late%20September%2C%20a%20few%20large%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-disrupting-denmark-airports-near-f-35-stealth-fighter-base-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrones%20were%20spotted%3C%2Fa%3E%20flying%20near%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20takeoffs%20and%20landings%20were%20halted%20for%20almost%20four%20hours.%20More%20than%2050%20flights%20were%20diverted%2C%20and%20over%20100%20more%20were%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%2030%20flights%20were%20disrupted%20at%20Oslo%20Airport%20in%20Norway%20due%20to%20another%20suspected%20drone%20sighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20several%20more%20European%20cities%20have%20seen%20nearby%20drones%20temporarily%20shut%20down%20their%20airports.%20It%20happened%20twice%20within%2024%20hours%20in%20Munich%20in%20early%20October.%20Over%2010%2C000%20people%20have%20had%20their%20travel%20plans%20disrupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20sense%2C%20this%20is%20a%20nuisance%20for%20travelers.%20However%2C%20analysts%20and%20political%20leaders%20say%20it's%20an%20example%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworsening-russian-hybrid-warfare-in-us-european-elections-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20hybrid%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20involves%20using%20plausible%20deniability%20to%20undermine%20a%20society%20and%20can%20also%20include%20disinformation%20and%20cyberattacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Blaise%20Metreweli%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20UK's%20Secret%20Intelligence%20Service%2C%20said%20in%20her%20inaugural%20speech%20on%20December%2015%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20frontline%20is%20everywhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20also%20been%20spotted%20near%20air%20bases%2C%20but%20the%20impact%20has%20been%20most%20palpable%20in%20Lithuania%2C%20the%20Baltic%20nation%20of%20less%20than%203%20million%20people%2C%20whose%20eastern%20border%20is%20less%20than%2070%20miles%20as%20the%20crow%20flies%20from%20Russia's%20westernmost%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2010%20weeks%2C%20the%20airport%20in%20Vilnius%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20has%20been%20shut%20down%2015%20times.%20And%20not%20due%20to%20drones%2C%20but%20balloons%20smuggling%20crates%20of%20cheap%20cigarettes%20over%20the%20border%20from%20Belarus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20also%20difficult%20to%20detect%20because%20they're%20not%20big%20aircraft%20or%20drones%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sean%20Patrick%2C%20senior%20aviation%20security%20analyst%20at%20Osprey%20Flight%20Solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20clever%20exploiting%20this%20from%20the%20Russian%20side%20to%20use%20these%20systems%2C%20and%20they've%20pushed%20Lithuania%20to%20declare%20this%20emergency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirteen%20days%20before%20the%20Scandinavia%20incidents%2C%20around%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoland-shot-down-russian-drones-violated-airspace-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20flew%20across%20the%20border%20into%20Poland.%20The%20airspace%20over%20four%20Polish%20airports%20was%20closed%20while%20NATO%20forces%20scrambled%20jets%2C%20shooting%20down%20up%20to%20four%20of%20the%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoland%20also%20invoked%20Article%204%20of%20the%20NATO%20treaty%2C%20which%C2%A0calls%20for%20consultation%20over%20an%20urgent%20situation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0its%20first%20usage%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20War%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20Russia-linked%20ship%20was%20located%20off%20the%20Danish%20coast%20during%20the%20Copenhagen%20incident.%20The%20French%20military%20later%20boarded%20the%20oil%20tanker%2C%20and%20the%20captain%2C%20a%20Chinese%20national%2C%20was%20char