tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongressional-stock-trade-ban-efforts-heating-up-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnna%20Paulina%20Luna%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Florida%20moved%20to%20force%20a%20vote%20on%20that%20bill%20by%20filing%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdischarge%20petition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20measure%2C%20which%20lawmakers%20have%20deployed%20with%20increasing%20success%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20forces%20the%20House%20to%20a%20vote%20on%20a%20bill%20if%20218%20lawmakers%20sign%20on%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20speaker%20is%20opposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20publication%2C%2015%20Republicans%20and%2059%20Democrats%20have%20signed%20onto%20Luna's%20discharge%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20left%3A%20Reps.%20Seth%20Magaziner%2C%20Brian%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%2C%20Anna%20Paulina%20Luna%2C%20and%20Chip%20Roy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6949c49304eda4732f2e02db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20left%3A%20Reps.%20Seth%20Magaziner%2C%20Brian%20Fitzpatrick%2C%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%2C%20Anna%20Paulina%20Luna%2C%20and%20Chip%20Roy.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FJonathan%20Ernst%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20issues%20with%20Luna's%20effort.%20Democrats%20have%20complained%20that%20Luna's%20resolution%20can't%20be%20amended%2C%20and%20she%20moved%20to%20introduce%20the%20measure%20before%20other%20stock%20trading%20ban%20proponents%20were%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appreciate%20that%20Rep.%20Luna%20supports%20our%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20Magaziner%20said%20earlier%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BShe%20jumped%20the%20gun%20a%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Roy%20%E2%80%94%20the%20chief%20GOP%20cosponsor%20of%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20has%20not%20signed%20onto%20the%20discharge%20petition%2C%20saying%20that%20for%20