0Democrats%20began%20to%20insist%20that%20the%20president%20and%20vice%20president%20be%20included%20as%20well%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20president%20exercises%20control%20over%20regulatory%20agencies%20and%20has%20access%20to%20more%20nonpublic%20information%20than%20members%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20zero%20justification%20and%20rationale%20for%20allowing%20a%20president%20of%20any%20party%2C%20or%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20any%20party%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20engage%20in%20stock%20trading%20while%20they%20have%20the%20awesome%20power%20of%20the%20presidency%2C%20vice%20presidency%2C%20and%20executive%20branch%20in%20their%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffries%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20request%20of%20Democratic%20leadership%2C%20Magaziner%20introduced%20a%20new%20stock%20trading%20ban%20bill%20last%20week%20that%20includes%20the%20president%20and%20vice%20president%2C%20and%20he%20plans%20to%20file%20a%20new%20discharge%20petition%20on%20that%20bill%20soon%20%E2%80%94%20though%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Balso%20continue%20to%20support%20and%20advocate%20for%26quot%3B%20Luna's%20discharge%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20publication%2C%20no%20Republicans%20have%20signed%20onto%20the%20new%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHedtler-Gaudette%20said%20he%20believed%20that%20the%20expanded%20bill%20was%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20kill%20the%20effort%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20contingent%20of%20the%20caucus%20on%20the%20Democratic%20side%2C%20and%20the%20conference%20on%20the%20Republican%20side%2C%20who%20on%20the%20substance%20and%20the%20merits%2C%20do%20not%20want%20to%20ban%20stock%20trading%20in%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20Hedlter-Gaudette%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20they'll%20use%20whatever%20kind%20of%20rhetorical%20kind%20of%20argument%20is%20closest%20to%20hand%20to%20justify.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20respond%20to%20that%20charge%2C%20a%20senior%20Democratic%20aide%20said%20that%20Luna's%20discharge%20petition%20was%20%26quot%3Bunsound%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20unamendable%20nature%20of%20her%20petition%20%26quot%3Bwould%20leave%20critical%20flaws%20in%20place%20and%20the%20calls%20for%20real%20accountability%20across%20government%20unanswered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20House%20Democrat%20who%20signed%20the%20discharge%20petition%2C%20granted%20anonymity%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20be%20candid%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20understood%20both%20the%20practical%20and%20political%20aspects%20of%20leadership's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20after%2C%20like%2C%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene's%20%2410%2C000%20transactions%20while%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20making%20millions%20of%20dollars%20off%20of%20cryptocurrency%20is%20like%20going%20after%20parking%20tickets%20when%20you%20have%20people%20committing%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20leadership%2C%20I'm%20thinking%2C%20what%3F%20No%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20moral%20equivalence%20between%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20Donald%20Trump.%20He%20is%20uniquely%20and%20utterly%20corrupt%2C%20and%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20messaging%20for%20the%20midterms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanna-paulina-luna-discharge-petition-ban-stock-trading-congress-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1766660221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F693734677ecd1d1da66322d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanna-paulina-luna-discharge-petition-ban-stock-trading-congress-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rep.%20Anna%20Paulina%20Luna%20is%20trying%20to%20force%20a%20vote%20on