0Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20giants%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Google%20DeepMind%20are%20competing%20for%20top%20talent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20companies%20are%20offering%20huge%20pay%20packages%20for%20the%20best%20and%20brightest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20are%20also%20paying%20top%20dollar%20for%20new%20talent%20through%20internships%2C%20fellowships%2C%20and%20residencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20race%20to%20develop%20AI%2C%20the%20humble%20internship%20is%20not%20so%20humble%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pay%20for%20short-term%2C%20entry-level%20roles%20in%20AI%20now%20rivals%20full-time%20salaries%20in%20other%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20heavyweights%20competing%20to%20develop%20artificial%20intelligence%20have%20famously%20offered%20top%20researchers%20and%20engineers%20enormous%20pay%20packages%20in%20what's%20been%20described%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-mustafa-suleyman-talent-wars-pay-packages-salaries-meta-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20talent%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20Meta%20spent%20%2414.3%20billion%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpay-cuts-poaching-pivoting-inside-scale-ai-meta-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvestment%20in%20Scale%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deal%20widely%20seen%20as%20an%20acquihire%20of%20CEO%20Alexandr%20Wang.%20Google%20made%20its%20own%20move%2C%20acquiring%20Windsurf's%20top%20talent%20for%20%242.4%20billion.%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20said%20that%20Meta%20tried%20to%20lure%20employees%20away%20with%20%24100%20million%20signing%20bonuses%2C%20an%20effort%20that%20Meta%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20said%20OpenAI%20later%20matched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20at%20smaller%20startups%2C%20AI%20leaders%20can%20command%20between%20%24300%2C000%20and%20%24400%2C000%20in%20base%20pay%2C%20Shawn%20Thorne%2C%20managing%20director%20at%20executive%20search%20firm%20True%20Search%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20landing%20established%20talent%20is%20driving%20big%20spending%2C%20however%2C%20the%20top%20AI%20companies%20are%20also%20throwing%20significant%20sums%20at%20discovering%20new%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20some%20of%20the%20top-paying%20internships%2C%20fellowships%2C%20and%20residency%20programs%20in%202026%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%2C%20and%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnthropic%20Safety%20Fellow%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223527%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22llustration%20by%20ANTHROPIC%2C%20August%201%2C%202025.%20Anthropic%20is%20an%20American%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20(intelligence%20artificielle%20(IA)%20company%20founded%20in%202021.%20It%20develops%20Claude%2C%20a%20family%20of%20large%20language%20models%2C%20and%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20research%20in%20AI%20safety%2C%20particularly%20interpretability.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6943419864858d02d217043d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERICCARDO%20MILANI%2FHans%20Lucas%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anthropic%20AI%20Safety%20Fellows%20Program%20is%20a%20four-month%2C%20full-time%20research%20fellowship%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20accelerate%20AI%20safety%20research%20and%20foster%20research%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20program%20is%20to%20help%20fellows%20produce%20public%20research.%20Over%2080%25%20of%20fellows%20in%20past%20classes%20have%20produced%20papers%2C%20Anthropic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20will%20receive%20direct%20mentorship%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-power-list-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleading%20AI%20researchers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20Jan%20Leike%2C%20Sam%20Bowman%2C%20Sara%20Price%2C%20Alex%20Tamkin%2C%20and%20Nina%20Panickssery.%20They'll%20receive%20a%20weekly%20stipend%20of%20%243%2C850%2C%20and%20another%20%2415%2C000%20a%20month%20for%20compute%20funding%2C%20as%20well%20as%20workspace%20access%20in%20Berkeley%20or%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplications%20for%20the%20next%20cohorts%20%E2%80%94%20which%20begin%20in%20May%20and%20July%202026%20%E2%80%94%20are%20open%20until%20January%2012%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20apply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjob-boards.greenhouse.io%2Fanthropic%2Fjobs%2F5023394008%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20OpenAI%20Residency%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224307%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22OpenAI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F694341ab64858d02d2170441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20Residency%20is%20a%20six-month%20program%20that%20brings%20participants%20into%20the%20organization%20as%20full-time%20employees%20to%20work%20alongside%20research%20teams%20on%20advanced%20AI%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20are%20integrated%20into%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstatistics-from-openai-analysis-of-ai-impact-in-the-workplace-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20teams%2C%20where%20they%20work%20on%20%26quot%3Bambitious%20projects%20that%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20receive%20mentorship%2C%20contribute%20to%20ongoing%20research%2C%20and%20may%20be%20considered%20for%20full-time%20roles%20after%20the%20program.%20Residents%20receive%20%2418%2C300%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20is%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20Candidates%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20strong%20programming%20skills%2C%20a%20solid%20foundation%20in%20advanced%20mathematics%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20execute%20complex%20technical%20projects%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20that%20it%20expects%20to%20review%20applications%20and%20begin%20interviewing%20as%20early%20as%20January%202026.%20Interviews%20are%20likely%20to%20involve%20multiple%20technical%20assessments%2C%20and%20residency%20start%20dates%20are%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20apply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fcareers%2Fresidency-2026-san-francisco%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGoogle%20Student%20Researcher%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Google%20logo%20is%20seen%20at%20a%20company%20research%20facility%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6938e2b704d0f0a114f1b957%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Barria%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20accepting%20applications%20for%20its%20Student%20Researcher%20Program%20on%20a%20rolling%20basis%2C%20with%20the%20window%20expected%20to%20remain%20open%20until%20July%2017%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20targets%20US-based%20Ph.D.%20students%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20related%20fields%2C%20offering%20flexible%2C%20project-based%20research%20roles%20across%20teams%2C%20including%20Google%20DeepMind%20and%20Google%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20will%20be%20based%20in%20one%20of%20several%20locations%20in%20the%20US%20and%20will%20work%20on%20exploratory%20projects%20%26quot%3Bthat%20drive%20scientific%20advancement%20across%20a%20multitude%20of%20research%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20says%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3