tive%20order%20directing%20the%20education%20secretary%20to%20redefine%20what%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20service%26quot%3B%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20hear%20about%20the%20challenges%2C%20successes%2C%20and%20unique%20experiences%20you're%20facing%20with%20your%20student%20loans.%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20student-loan%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flnkd.in%2FeDDHUjmJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20form%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20we'll%20be%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ed.gov%2Fmedia%2Fdocument%2Ffact-sheet-restoring-public-service-loan-forgiveness-its-statutory-purpose-october-30-2025-112456.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20fact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20department%20said%20that%20the%20rule%20will%20change%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20qualifying%20employer%20%26quot%3Bto%20exclude%20employers%20that%20participate%20in%20illegal%20activities%20such%20that%20they%20have%20a%20substantial%20illegal%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20rule%20is%20set%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20in%20July%202026%2C%20and%20some%20student-loan%20servicers%20that%20collect%20payments%20from%20borrowers%20in%20PSLF%20have%20said%20that%20nothing%20is%20changing%20yet%2C%20and%20borrowers%20will%20receive%20updates%20as%20the%20regulations%20go%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20there%20are%20no%20impacts%20to%20borrowers%2C%20payment%20counts%2C%20or%20discharges%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20servicer%2C%20Aidvantage%2C%20posted%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20that%20the%20changes%20are%20intended%20to%20ensure%20that%20borrowers%20who%20receive%20PSLF%20have%20employers%20that%20contribute%20to%20public%20service%20and%20do%20not%20violate%20any%20laws.%20However%2C%20borrowers%20and%20advocates%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20the%20changes%20to%20eligibility%20will%20block%20public%20servants%20from%20relief%20because%20their%20employers%20do%20not%20align%20with%20the%20administration's%20political%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20new%20rule%2C%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20is%20refocusing%20the%20PSLF%20program%20to%20ensure%20federal%20benefits%20go%20to%20our%20Nation's%20teachers%2C%20first%20responders%2C%20and%20civil%20servants%20who%20tirelessly%20serve%20their%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20Nicholas%20Kent%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c224c75d-630c-4ed6-bed8-00b3f71b1983%5C%22%3EWhat's%20set%20to%20change%20for%20PSLF%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20change%20in%20the%20PSLF%20rule%20concerns%20eligibility%20for%20PSLF%20employers.%20While%20any%20public%20service%20employer%20previously%20qualified%20for%20the%20program%2C%20a%20fact%20sheet%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20changing%20the%20definition%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bqualifying%20employer%26quot%3B%20to%20exclude%20employers%20that%20have%20participated%20in%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20illegal%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20department%20said%20includes%20actions%20supporting%20terrorism%20or%20gender%20affirming%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20department%20determines%20that%20an%20employer%20engaged%20in%20illegal%20activity%2C%20affected%20employers%20will%20be%20notified%20and%20receive%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rebut%20the%20department's%20findings.%20Borrowers%20will%20also%20be%20notified%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20appeal%20the%20findings%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20the%20employer%20be%20disqualified%20from%20PSLF%2C%20they%20can%20reapply%20to%20be%20a%20qualifying%20employer%20within%2010%20years%2C%20or%20they%20can%20enter%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorrective%20action%20plan%26quot%3B%20with%20terms%20agreed%20upon%20by%20the%20department.%20Once%20an%20employer%20is%20deemed%20ineligible%2C%20any%20payments%20borrowers%20make%20while%20under%20that%20employer%20will%20not%20count%20toward%20PSLF%2C%20but%20retroactive%20payments%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-react-debt-relief-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20public%20service%20raised%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20looming%20PSLF%20changes.%20Megan%20Flocken%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20worker%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20counting%20my%20lucky%20stars%20that%20there's%20still%20the%20possibility%20that%20this%20PSLF%20program%20will%20remain%20intact%20because%20I%20have%20dedicated%20my%20whole%20professional%20life%20to%20public%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20department%20released%20its%20final%20rule%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20advocates%20and%20nonprofits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-sued-pslf-rule-limit-student-loan-forgiveness-new-lawsuit-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esued%20the%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20violating%20the%20law%20and%20harming%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20recruitment.%20Some%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20also%20called%20for%20the%20rule%20to%20be%20rescinded%3B%20Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSenSanders%2Fstatus%2F1984660457202852100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%201%20that%20the%20administration%20does%20%26quot%3Bnot%20have%20the%20right%20to%20take%20away%20student%20debt%20forgiveness%20from%20teachers%2C%20nurses%2C%20veterans%20and%20other%20public%20servants%20if%20they%20do%20not%20show%20loyalty%20to%20your%20right-wing%20political%20agenda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers